metadata.name: Rise of The Queen
metadata.description:
Everyone is constantly surprised by magic cards. The magic cards were able to locate the queen cards this time on the king's command after he lost his queen, making the king pleased in the process and immortalizing their deed in the Ethereum blockchain as a reward.

Edition 1/1
Length 00:00:47
Frame rate 30
1920 * 1072
Cardistry, edited in Adobe Premiere and Adobe Photoshop
